    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required level. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the team determined the remaining evidence base is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion for the non-cannulated construct under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending. Quantitative comparison metrics (percent difference and E/uval) passed pre-specified acceptance bounds for all three QoIs.",
